comments: At the end of the drive Butler (MIA) gathers on his right foot and takes two legal steps prior to the release of his shot.
Prince (BKN) slightly extends his arms into Adebayo (MIA) as he is releasing from the screen but the contact is marginal.
Adebayo (MIA) maintains his pivot foot after controlling the loose ball.
Harris (BKN) briefly grasps Dragic's (MIA) arm, but does not affect his FOM off ball.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (BKN) and absorbs the contact.
Adebayo (MIA) briefly grasps Chandler's (BKN) jersey, but does not affect his FOM.
Chandler (BKN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Nunn (MIA) and absorbs the contact.
LeVert (BKN) commits a take foul on Butler (MIA).
Dinwiddie (BKN) commits the personal take foul on Butler (MIA).
Harris (BKN) makes incidental foot contact with Adebayo (MIA) during the screen.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Dinwiddie (BKN) throws the ball out of bounds.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) delivers contact to Dragic's (MIA) body after receiving the inbounds pass.
